-\partial V/\partial t = \min_{u(t)} \{x^TQx + u^TRu + \partial V^T/\partial x(Ax + Bu) \}
x \in \Re^n
u \in \Re^m
Q \in \Re^{n\times n}
R \in \Re^{m\times m}
A \in \Re^{n\times n}
B \in \Re^{n\times m}
u
u^*=-\frac{1}{2}R^{-1}B^T\partial V/\partial x
V(x,t)
x
V(x(t),t) = x(t)^{T}P(t)x(t)
\partial V/\partial x = 2P(t)x(t)
u^*(t) = -R^{-1}B^TP(t)x(t)
P
-\partial V/\partial t = -x^T\dot{P}x \equiv x^TQx + (-R^{-1}B^TPx)^TR(-R^{-1}B^TPx)+2x^TP(Ax+B[-R^{-1}B^TPx])
-x^T\dot{P}x = x^T\{A^TP + PA + Q - PBR^{-1}B^TP\}x
A^TP
PA
2x^TP
Ax+Bu^*
P
P = QLQ^T
Q
\begin{align*} A^TP+PA &= A^TQLQ^T + QLQ^TA \\ Q^TA^TP+Q^TPA &= Q^TA^TQLQ^T+LQ^TA \\ Q^TA^TPQ+Q^TPAQ &= Q^TA^TQL+LQ^TAQ \\ Q^T(A^TP+PA)Q &=Q^TA^TQL+(Q^TAQ)^TL \\  &= Q^TA^TQL+Q^TA^TQL \\  &= 2(Q^TA^TQ)L \end{align*} 
Q
\begin{align*} A^TP+PA &= 2Q(Q^TA^TQ)LQ^T \\  &= 2A^T(QLQ^T)\\  &= 2A^TP \\  &= 2PA \end{align*} 
P
P^T=P
